==Description==
The '''Silver Powder''' is a type of [[Held Items|Held Item]] that can only be equipped to [[File:Bug_Type_icon.png|30px]]Bug type Pokémon.

==Details==
Raises the attack of the Pokémon holding the Item by 10%.

